sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant Domain as SharedGame
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events
    participant Notif as UserNotifications
    participant Badge as BadgeService

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/shared-games/{id}/approve-publication

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract gameId
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create ApproveSharedGamePublicationCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Verify admin role
    Validator->>DB: Check game exists
    DB-->>Validator: Game found ✓
    Validator->>Validator: Verify Status = PendingApproval
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get SharedGame
    DB-->>Handler: SharedGame (Status: PendingApproval)

    Handler->>Domain: game.Approve(adminId)
    Domain->>Domain: Status = Published
    Domain->>Domain: PublishedAt = UtcNow
    Domain->>Domain: ApprovedBy = adminId
    Domain->>Events: Raise GamePublishedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(game)
    DB-->>Handler: Game updated ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish GamePublishedEvent

    Events->>Notif: Send approval notification to submitter
    Notif->>Notif: Create notification
    Notif->>Notif: Send email

    Events->>Badge: Check badge eligibility
    Badge->>DB: Get submitter contribution count
    DB-->>Badge: Count = 10
    Badge->>Badge: Check "10 Games Published" badge
    Badge->>Events: Publish BadgeEarnedEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: SharedGameDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: SharedGameDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {id, status: "Published", publishedAt}
